OL,3,CFamily of Lilly Jones pay tribute to
OL,4,Cher as 'the most beautiful little girl'
OL,6,FThe family of Lilly Anne Jones has
OL,7,Fpaid tribute to her, describing her as
OL,8,F"the most beautiful, kind and caring
OL,9,Flittle girl".
OL,11,FThe body of the 14-year-old was found
OL,12,Fin the Duffryn Park area of Blaina on
OL,13,FJune 22 after she was reported missing
OL,14,Ftwo days earlier.
OL,16,FAn inquest opening at Gwent Coroner's
OL,17,FCourt on Monday (6 July) heard the
OL,18,Fteenager was found multiple stab
OL,19,Fwounds, including injuries to her
OL,20,Fchest and neck.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/5
