OL,3,CFamily of Lilly Jones pay tribute to
OL,4,Cher as 'the most beautiful little girl'
OL,6,FA 14-year-old boy from the Blaenau
OL,7,FGwent area, who cannot be named for
OL,8,Flegal reasons, has been charged with
OL,9,Fher murder.
OL,11,FA trial date has been set on 23
OL,12,FNovember which is estimated to last
OL,13,Ffour weeks.
OL,15,FA plea and trial preparation hearing
OL,16,Fhas been set for 24 July.
OL,18,FThe family of Lilly Jones said:
OL,20,F"As a family, the word 'heartbroken'
OL,21,Fdoesn't come close to what we feel.
OL,26,@|D@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/5
