OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,451,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1783959568
OL,3,CFamily of Lilly Jones pay tribute to
OL,4,Cher as 'the most beautiful little girl'
OL,6,F"We'd like to focus more on Lilly and
OL,7,Fwhat a beautiful person she is rather
OL,8,Fthan the horrific thing she's been
OL,9,Fforced to endure.
OL,11,F"Lilly is the most beautiful, kind and
OL,12,Fcaring little girl we had the
OL,13,Fprivilege to call our daughter,
OL,14,Fsister, granddaughter, niece, cousin
OL,15,Fand friend.
OL,17,F"She is completely and utterly
OL,18,Fherself, she's quirky and confident,
OL,19,Fsassy and dramatic and loves her music.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,451,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1783959568
OL,3,CFamily of Lilly Jones pay tribute to
OL,4,Cher as 'the most beautiful little girl'
OL,6,F"Her eclectic taste in music took us
OL,7,Ffrom My Chemical Romance to Kate Bush
OL,8,Fand absolutely unapologetically sang
OL,9,Fevery word on the top of her voice, no
OL,10,Fmatter who's listening.
OL,12,F"We could write a book about how
OL,13,Famazing and accepting of all types of
OL,14,Fpeople she is, advocating for anyone
OL,15,Fwho needed her to.
OL,17,F"Our loss has left an unimaginable
OL,18,Fhole in not only our lives but in the
OL,19,Fwhole community.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/5
